r 30 min, 95<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C for 5 min and then ramp down to 25<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C at 5<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C per min. After annealing the gRNA can be directly cloned into L2_gRNA-CAs9-CsA or L2_gRNA-CsA plasmids without the need of any further processing.<\/span><\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":null,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":783033,"guid":"5B827880A80911E9BC5C3D209D22A6C6","previous_id":783032,"previous_guid":"1B5BBDC0A80911E9BC5C3D209D22A6C6","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"AB768EAAF9064A53ACDD12999132D8B4","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"0D38EF7024D147B0891486BF22127DF9","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;:UNDERLINE;\">Cloning into backbone vector <\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">In a 0.2 mL tube set up the following reaction:<\/div><table border><tr style = \"text-align:center;\"><td>  <\/td><td>A<\/td><td>B<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">1<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  <b>Component<\/b>\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  <b>Volume (<\/b>\u03bcL<b>)<\/b>\n  <\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">2<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  &nbsp;  Sterile water\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">5<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">3<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  10x Tango buffer (Thermo Fisher)\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">4<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  &nbsp;&nbsp; 1 mg\/mL bovine serum albumin\n  (NEB)\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  &nbsp;&nbsp; 0.5 \n  <\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">5<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  T4 DNA ligase (5 U\/\u00b5L) (Thermo Fisher)\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  &nbsp; 0.25 \n  <\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">6<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  10mM ATP (SIGMA)\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 \n  <\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">7<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  SapI (LguI) (5 U\/\u00b5L) (Thermo Fisher)\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  0.25 \n  <\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">8<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">L2_393-Csa (25-50 ng)<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">9<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">annealed oligo<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1<\/td><\/tr><tr><td style = \"text-align:center;\">10<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">  Final volume\n  <\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">10<\/td><\/tr><\/table><div class = \"text-block\"><ul style = \"list-style-type:disc;\"><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"> Place samples on the thermocycler and incubated using the following program: <\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><span>Assembly:     15 cycles: 3 minutes at 37<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C and 4 minutes at 16<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C <\/span><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><span>Termination: 5 minutes at 50<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C and 10 minutes at 80<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C <\/span><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"> Transform chemically competent using 1 \u03bcL of reaction and plate on LB agar plates with 100 \u03bcg\/mL spec and X-gal 40. Incubate at 37 oC for 16 h.<\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"> Confirm with sequencing<\/li><\/ul><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Assembly:     15 cycles: 3 minutes at 37<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C and 4 minutes at 16<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C <\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Termination: 5 minutes at 50<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C and 10 minutes at 80<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">o<\/span><span>C <\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><ul style = \"list-style-type:disc;\"><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"> Transform chemically competent using 1 \u03bcL of reaction and plate on LB agar plates with 100 \u03bcg\/mL spec and X-gal 40. Incubate at 37 oC for 16 h.<\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"> Confirm with sequencing<\/li><\/ul><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><ul style = \"list-style-type:disc;\"><\/ul><\/div><\/div>"}},{"id":1054725,"guid":"7D13DB3210FF462394C78F8D8F5A4E97","order_id":2,"type_